OL,3,CWorld's oldest book copy of The
OL,4,COdyssey goes on display in UK library
OL,6,FA 1,700-year-old copy of Homer's The
OL,7,FOdyssey has returned to a UK library
OL,8,Fafter a top-secret trip to New York as
OL,9,FSir Christopher Nolan's epic hits
OL,10,Fcinema screens.
OL,12,FThe rare 3rd century text, which forms
OL,13,Fthe centrepiece of 'The Manchester
OL,14,FOdyssey' exhibition at John Rylands
OL,15,FLibrary, Manchester is the world's
OL,16,Foldest surviving book copy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
