PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784895504
OL,3,CWorld's oldest book copy of The
OL,4,COdyssey goes on display in UK library
OL,6,FIts arrival follows a high-profile
OL,7,Fpromotional tour with Universal
OL,8,FPictures for the blockbuster film The
OL,9,FOdyssey, where library curators joined
OL,10,Fthe movie's cast on press junkets
OL,11,Facross London and New York.
OL,13,FNow, one of the world's rarest
OL,14,Fliterary treasures has gone on public
OL,15,Fdisplay in Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
