PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784895504
OL,3,CWorld's oldest book copy of The
OL,4,COdyssey goes on display in UK library
OL,6,FThe parchment manuscript is housed in
OL,7,Fthe Collections Gallery, with its
OL,8,Funveiling timed just two days ahead of
OL,9,Fthe global cinematic release of
OL,10,FNolan's highly anticipated film
OL,11,Fadaptation.
OL,13,FThe fragments, written in ancient
OL,14,FGreek, are the oldest existing version
OL,15,Fof the poem arranged into a book.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
