PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784895504
OL,3,CWorld's oldest book copy of The
OL,4,COdyssey goes on display in UK library
OL,6,FCopied in Egypt during the 3rd century
OL,7,FCE - an era when readers were first
OL,8,Ftransitioning from rolled scrolls to
OL,9,Fbound pages - the ancient manuscript
OL,10,Fdetails Odysseus' 10-year struggle to
OL,11,Freturn home after the Trojan War.
OL,13,FIn a "groundbreaking" move for a
OL,14,Funiversity library, the institution
OL,15,Fpartnered directly with Universal
OL,16,FPictures to place the ancient text at
OL,17,Fthe heart of the film's publicity
OL,18,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
