CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784895504
OL,3,CWorld's oldest book copy of The
OL,4,COdyssey goes on display in UK library
OL,6,FProfessor Christopher Pressler,
OL,7,FUniversity Librarian, and Dr Jeremy
OL,8,FPenner, Curator of African and Near
OL,9,FEastern Manuscripts, flew to New York
OL,10,Fand London to participate in official
OL,11,Fpress junkets, presenting the
OL,12,Fpriceless document to the film's cast
OL,13,Fand directors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
