PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784895504
OL,3,CWorld's oldest book copy of The
OL,4,COdyssey goes on display in UK library
OL,6,F"From a third-century manuscript of
OL,7,FHomer's Odyssey appearing alongside
OL,8,Fone of the year's biggest film
OL,9,Freleases, to rare Egyptian papyri in
OL,10,FTexas and the Ian Curtis archive in
OL,11,FNew York, our collections are reaching
OL,12,Faudiences on a truly international
OL,13,Fscale," Pressler said.
OL,15,F"These projects demonstrate the
OL,16,Fextraordinary cultural power of
OL,17,FSpecial Collections and what it means
OL,18,Fto be 'From Manchester, for the world'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
